<h3>6 Player Game ~4 turns<br>
</h3>
Start with:<br>
1st Latin War, Tarquinius, Junius<br>
3 Senators per player X 6 = 18 Senators<br>
2 Red Cards per player X 6 = 12 Red Cards<br>
<br>
Deck:<br>
8 Red Cards<br>
11 Black Cards<br>
19 Total Cards<br>
Red = 42%; War = 21%<br>
